results.deck: Remedy Entertainment is a small game development studio based in Espoo, Finland. Best known for their critically acclaimed Max Payne series, Remedy's most recent games are Death Rally, an iOS remake of their very first game, and Alan Wake's American Nightmare, a continuation of their Xbox 360 exclusive Alan Wake.
results.description:
Games

  • 1996 - Death Rally (PC, currently available as freeware)
  • 2001 - Max Payne (PC, Playstation 2, Xbox, Mac)
  • 2003 - Max Payne 2: The Fall of Max Payne (PC, PlayStation 2, Xbox)
  • 2010 - Alan Wake (Xbox 360)
  • 2011 - Death Rally (iPhone, iPod Touch, iPad) - Developed by Cornfox & Bros Ltd and Mountain Sheep, published by Remedy
  • 2012 - Alan Wake's American Nightmare (PC, XBLA)
